Package: Rthoptera
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of acoustic signals from insects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
            person("Francisco", "Rivas", email = "frivasfu@purdue.edu",
                    role = c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1256-2225")),
            person("Cesare", "Brizio", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Francisco Rivas  <fcorivasf@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides a set of interactive functions (each one is a Shiny App) to analyze insect acoustic signals, including preprocessing (e.g., high-pass filter, remove DC offset, down-sampling, etc.). Analytical functions allow the user to automatically extract relevant acoustic features in both spectral and temporal dimensions. 
